{"type":"file-history-snapshot","messageId":"7381abdf-fdd3-4668-a62b-f1a1b11d480d","snapshot":{"messageId":"7381abdf-fdd3-4668-a62b-f1a1b11d480d","trackedFileBackups":{},"timestamp":"2026-03-28T07:29:28.056Z"},"isSnapshotUpdate":false}
{"parentUuid":"92d796eb-88b9-4a38-a554-b3c58c6a14d5","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"7a5de78e-3569-49a1-9118-9843361b02e8","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"compose は開発環境ようなので一旦パスワードは問題ないです。そのほかのものについて解説してもらっていいですか"},"uuid":"7381abdf-fdd3-4668-a62b-f1a1b11d480d","timestamp":"2026-03-28T07:29:27.921Z","permissionMode":"acceptEdits","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"f2cb982d-a51c-4873-9c04-5116e8252779","version":"2.1.84","gitBranch":"postgres-18"}
{"parentUuid":"7381abdf-fdd3-4668-a62b-f1a1b11d480d","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_018XJ3KQks6J4jC6jCLW5izE","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1075,"cache_read_input_tokens":30928,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1075},"output_tokens":59,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"}},"requestId":"req_011CZV5tqkT3BbM7QQVSS5DR","type":"assistant","uuid":"a73d67f5-2af4-419a-8b64-ba7dfe237402","timestamp":"2026-03-28T07:29:29.851Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"f2cb982d-a51c-4873-9c04-5116e8252779","version":"2.1.84","gitBranch":"postgres-18"}
{"parentUuid":"a73d67f5-2af4-419a-8b64-ba7dfe237402","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_018XJ3KQks6J4jC6jCLW5izE","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"了解しました。開発環境ということで、それ以外の改善点を詳しく解説します。\n\n## 1. **ボリュームパス** (`/var/lib/postgresql` → `/var/lib/postgresql/data`)\n\n```yaml\n# 現在\nvolumes:\n  - postgres_data:/var/lib/postgresql\n\n# 改善\nvolumes:\n  - postgres_data:/var/lib/postgresql/data\n```\n\n**理由：**\n- PostgreSQL の実際のデータは `/var/lib/postgresql/data` に格納されます\n- `/var/lib/postgresql` 直下にはメタデータファイルなども含まれているため、マウントポイントを明確にすることで意図が明確になります\n\n---\n\n## 2. **ヘルスチェック**\n\n```yaml\nhealthcheck:\n  test: [\"CMD-SHELL\", \"pg_isready -U postgres\"]\n  interval: 10s        # 10秒ごとにチェック\n  timeout: 5s          # 5秒以内に応答なければ失敗\n  retries: 5           # 5回失敗したらunhealthy\n```\n\n**メリット：**\n- Docker Compose で `depends_on` を使う際に `condition: service_healthy` で待機できます\n- APIサーバーがDBの起動完了を待ってから起動できるため、接続エラーを防げます\n- 実装例：\n  ```yaml\n  api:\n    depends_on:\n      db:\n        condition: service_healthy\n  ```\n\n---\n\n## 3. **再起動ポリシー** (`restart: unless-stopped`)\n\n```yaml\nrestart: unless-stopped\n```\n\n**動作：**\n- コンテナが異常終了しても自動的に再起動\n- 手動で `docker-compose down` で停止した場合は、再起動されない（`always` と異なる点）\n\n**開発環境での利点：**\n- DBのメモリ不足などで落ちた場合、自動復旧されます\n- 予期しない停止からの回復が自動化される\n\n---\n\n## 4. **リソース制限** (`deploy.resources.limits`)\n\n```yaml\ndeploy:\n  resources:\n    limits:\n      cpus: \"1\"          # 最大1コアのCPU使用\n      memory: 512M       # 最大512MBメモリ\n```\n\n**重要性：**\n- メモリリークやクエリ暴走がOSを巻き込まない\n- ローカル開発環境のマシンを保護\n- 本番環境との差異を意識した開発ができる\n\n開発環境なので厳しい制限にする必要はありませんが、デフォルトで無制限だとマシンが重くなる可能性があります。\n\n---\n\n**改善版compose.yml：**\n\n```yaml\nservices:\n  db:\n    image: postgres:18\n    environment:\n      POSTGRES_USER: postgres\n      POSTGRES_PASSWORD: password\n      POSTGRES_DB: postgres\n    ports:\n      - \"5432:5432\"\n    volumes:\n      - postgres_data:/var/lib/postgresql/data\n    healthcheck:\n      test: [\"CMD-SHELL\", \"pg_isready -U postgres\"]\n      interval: 10s\n      timeout: 5s\n      retries: 5\n    restart: unless-stopped\n    deploy:\n      resources:\n        limits:\n          memory: 512M\n\nvolumes:\n  postgres_data:\n```\n\n反映してもよろしいですか？"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1075,"cache_read_input_tokens":30928,"output_tokens":1072,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1075,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZV5tqkT3BbM7QQVSS5DR","type":"assistant","uuid":"93959e88-bc2d-48dc-bb5b-eb2419c56ce5","timestamp":"2026-03-28T07:29:36.285Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"f2cb982d-a51c-4873-9c04-5116e8252779","version":"2.1.84","gitBranch":"postgres-18"}
